== 製作 ==
2012年3月23日，據傳[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]有意開發《[[冰血暴|冰血暴]]》電視劇版本。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/fx-eyes-series-adaptation-of-fargo-1118051861/|title=FX eyes series adaptation of ‘Fargo’|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Cynthia Littleton|date=2012-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-12|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312201433/http://variety.com/2012/tv/news/fx-eyes-series-adaptation-of-fargo-1118051861/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月24日，FX正式宣布將改編曾榮獲[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的1996年電影《冰血暴》，原[[電影導演|電影導演]][[科恩兄弟|柯恩兄弟]]將擔任執行製作，由《{{le|非凡女警|The Unusuals}}》、《{{le|我們這一代|My Generation (TV series)}}》主創[[諾亞·霍利|諾亞·霍利]]執筆並身兼執行製作，{{link-en|沃倫·理托菲爾德|Warren Littlefield}}亦將共同擔任執行製作，由[[米高梅電視公司|米高梅電視公司]]及[[福斯娛樂集團|FX製作公司]]共同製作。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/fx-teams-with-joel-ethan-coen-and-noah-hawley-for-series-adaptation-of-fargo/ |title=FX Teams With Joel & Ethan Coen And Noah Hawley For Series Adaptation Of 'Fargo' |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2012-09-21 |accessdate=2012-09-25 |archive-date=2012-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925182216/http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/fx-teams-with-joel-ethan-coen-and-noah-hawley-for-series-adaptation-of-fargo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年3月28日，FX正式預訂本劇作為電視網首部有限劇集，預計將有10集集數。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fx-orders-fargo-limited-series-431532|title=FX Orders 'Fargo' Limited Series from Noah Hawley, Coen Brothers|publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|author=Lacey Rose|date=2013-03-28|accessdate=2017-03-12|archive-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030011105/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fx-orders-fargo-limited-series-431532|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/03/fx-greenlights-fargo-limited-series-463214/|title=FX Greenlights ‘Fargo’ Limited Series, Lines Up Slew Of Event Series In Development|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2013-03-28|accessdate=2017-03-12|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313040538/http://deadline.com/2013/03/fx-greenlights-fargo-limited-series-463214/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2013/03/28/fargo-tv-series-fx/ |title='Fargo' TV Series Gets 10 Episodes On FX |publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]] |first=Terri |last=Schwartz |date=2013-03-28 |accessdate=2014-04-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423142051/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2013/03/28/fargo-tv-series-fx |archivedate=2014-04-23 }}</ref>5月29日，宣布《[[超級製作人|超級製作人]]》、《[[絕命毒師|絕命毒師]]》[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]得主{{link-en|亞當·伯恩斯坦|Adam Bernstein}}將執導首集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/05/adam-bernstein-to-direct-fxs-fargo-509822/|title=Adam Bernstein To Direct FX’s ‘Fargo’|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2013-05-29|accessdate=2017-03-12|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312195625/http://deadline.com/2013/05/adam-bernstein-to-direct-fxs-fargo-509822/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年秋天，本劇正式進入製作，並於[[艾伯塔|艾伯塔]][[卡爾加里|卡爾加里]]展開拍攝。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://voices.suntimes.com/arts-entertainment/the-daily-sizzle/billy-bob-thornton-to-star-in-fargo-series-on-fx/ |title=Billy Bob Thornton to star in 'Fargo' series on FX |work=Chicago Sun-Times |first=Lori |last=Rackl |date=2013-08-02 |accessdate=2014-04-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803163221/http://voices.suntimes.com/arts-entertainment/the-daily-sizzle/billy-bob-thornton-to-star-in-fargo-series-on-fx/ |archivedate=2014-08-03 }}</ref>

